1940;;Seven Sinners;;American;;Tay Garnett;;Marlene Dietrich, John Wayne;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seven_Sinners_(1940_film);;The film spotlights the controversial life of torch singer Bijou Blanche (Dietrich), who has been kicked off one South Seas island after another. She is accompanied by naval deserter Edward Patrick 'Little Ned' Finnegan (Broderick Crawford) and magician/pickpocket Sasha Mencken (Mischa Auer). Eventually, she meets a handsome, young naval officer, Lt. Dan Brent (Wayne), and the two fall in love. When Brent vows to marry Bijou, his commander and others plead with him to leave her.